{"title_page": "Aamaguhan, Chhattisgarh", "text_new": "'''Aamaguhan''' is an Indian village situated in the \u201cTehsil Bade Rajpur\u201d of District \u201cBastar\u201d of the state Chhattisgarh. It is a medium sized village that falls under the Gram Panchayat of Baijanpuri & BADERAJPUR (Janpad Panchayat) with Kondagaon (Zilla Panchayat).<ref>{{cite web |title=Village &#038; Panchayats District Kondagaon - Government of Chhattisgarh |url=https://kondagaon.gov.in/village-panchayats/ |website=kondagaon.gov.in}}</ref>\n==Government==\nIt falls under the Lok Sabha Constituency of \u201cBastar\u201d which is reserved for Scheduled Tribes (ST) candidates.\n==Population==\nAccording to the Indian Government Census of 2011, it has total 144 families were residing. The population was 658 of which 329 were males while 329 were females \n==References==\n\n[[Category:Villages]]\n[[Category:Indian Villages]]\n[[Category:District Bastar Villages]]\n[[Category:Chhattisgarh Villages]]\n", "text_old": "'''Aamaguhan''' is an Indian village situated in the \u201cTehsil Bade Rajpur\u201d of District \u201cBastar\u201d of the state Chhattisgarh. It is a medium sized village that falls under the Gram Panchayat of Baijanpuri & BADERAJPUR (Janpad Panchayat) with Kondagaon (Zilla Panchayat).<ref>{{cite web |title=Village &#038; Panchayats District Kondagaon - Government of Chhattisgarh |url=https://kondagaon.gov.in/village-panchayats/ |website=kondagaon.gov.in}}</ref>\n==Government==\nIt falls under the Lok Sabha Constituency of \u201cBastar\u201d which is reserved for Scheduled Tribes (ST) candidates.\n==Population==\nAccording to the Indian Government Census of 2011,\n==References==\n\n[[Category:Villages]]\n[[Category:Indian Villages]]\n[[Category:District Bastar Villages]]\n[[Category:Chhattisgarh Villages]]\n", "name_user": "Rajeev Gaur123", "label": "safe", "comment": "information updation", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aamaguhan,_Chhattisgarh"}
{"title_page": "Pavle Radovanovi\u0107", "text_new": "{{Infobox football official\n| name            = Pavle Radovanovi\u0107\n| image           = \n| caption         = \n| full_name       = Pavle Radovanovi\u0107\n| birth_date      = {{Birth date and age|1975|8|21|df=y}}\n| birth_place     = [[Yugoslavia]]\n| death_date      = \n| death_place     = \n| years1          = \n| league1         = [[Montenegrin First League]]\n| role1           = Referee\n| internationalyears1 = 2008\u2013\n| confederation1      = [[FIFA]] listed\n| internationalrole1  = Referee\n}}\n\n'''Pavle Radovanovi\u0107''' ([[Serbian Cyrillic alphabet|Serbian Cyrillic]]: \u041f\u0430\u0432\u043b\u0435 \u0420\u0430\u0434\u043e\u0432\u0430\u043d\u043e\u0432\u0438\u045b; born 21 August 1975) is a [[Montenegro|Montenegrin]] international [[Referee (association football)|referee]] who refereed at [[2014 FIFA World Cup qualification (UEFA)|2014 FIFA World Cup qualifiers]].<ref>[http://worldreferee.com/site/copy.php?linkID=1610&linkType=referee&contextType=bio Profile]</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|2}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Radovanovic, Pavle}}\n[[Category:1975 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Montenegrin football referees]]\n\n\n{{Montenegro-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football official\n| officialname    = Pavle Radovanovi\u0107\n| image           = \n| fullname        = Pavle Radovanovi\u0107\n| birth_date      = {{Birth date and age|1975|8|21|df=y}}\n| birth_place     = [[Yugoslavia]]\n| death_date      = \n| death_place     = \n| years1          = \n| league1         = [[Montenegrin First League]]\n| role1           = Referee\n| internationalyears1 = 2008\u2013\n| confederation1      = [[FIFA]] listed\n| internationalrole1  = Referee\n}}\n'''Pavle Radovanovi\u0107''' ([[Serbian Cyrillic alphabet|Serbian Cyrillic]]: \u041f\u0430\u0432\u043b\u0435 \u0420\u0430\u0434\u043e\u0432\u0430\u043d\u043e\u0432\u0438\u045b; born 21 August 1975) is a [[Montenegro|Montenegrin]] international [[Referee (association football)|referee]] who refereed at [[2014 FIFA World Cup qualification (UEFA)|2014 FIFA World Cup qualifiers]].<ref>[http://worldreferee.com/site/copy.php?linkID=1610&linkType=referee&contextType=bio Profile]</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|2}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Radovanovic, Pavle}}\n[[Category:1975 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Montenegrin football referees]]\n\n\n{{Montenegro-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Zyxw", "label": "safe", "comment": "update infobox to remove article from unknown parameter category", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pavle_Radovanovi%C4%87"}
